### JWT Authentication Test cho API Gateway

### Bước 1: Lấy JWT Token từ Auth Service
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/generate-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}

### Bước 2: Login với credentials
POST http://localhost:5050/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### Bước 3: Test endpoint KHÔNG có token (sẽ trả về 401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing

### Bước 4: Test endpoint CÓ token (thay YOUR_JWT_TOKEN bằng token từ bước 1 hoặc 2)
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Bước 5: Test POST endpoint với token
POST http://localhost:5050/pricing
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "basePrice": 1000,
  "quantity": 5,
  "taxRate": 0.1
}

### Bước 6: Test GET by ID với token
GET http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Bước 7: Test PUT với token
PUT http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPrice": 1500,
  "newPrice": 1800
}

### Bước 8: Test DELETE với token
DELETE http://localhost:5050/pricing/123
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Bước 9: Test Policy endpoint với token
GET http://localhost:5050/policy
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN